description:

description:
Esplanade Hotel Fremantle - by Rydges is located in the heart of Fremantle, overlooking Esplanade Park. 20 minutes' drive from central Perth, this hotel offers 2 outdoor pools and a fitness centre. A full buffet breakfast is available.

The hotel has 2 on-site restaurants with a great selection of international cuisine. The Atrium Garden Restaurant buffet serves a variety of special dishes, whilst The Harbour Master features tapas, grill and local seafood. Enjoy a drink in one of the 2 bars including, Marine Lounge Bar and the Ball & Chain with craft beer on tap and great pub-style food.

Guests enjoy a choice of spacious and comfortable guest rooms and suites, and some rooms offer a private balcony overlooking parklands. All rooms feature a 50-inch ULTRA HD LCD television with Streamcast

Esplanade Hotel by Rydges is within easy walking distance of local shops, restaurants, markets and museums. Fishing Boat Harbour is just 400 metres away and Fremantle Markets is just a 3-minute walk away. Perth International Airport is a 30-minute drive.

description:
Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle is a unique, boutique hotel, purpose-built using innovative sea container construction.

Fremantle Prison is a 10-minute walk away and Fremantle Markets is a 5-minute walk. The property is a 5-minute drive from the Western Australian Maritime Museum, and a 10-minute drive from Port Beach. Perth Airport is 40 minutes’ drive away.

Each stylish room at Hougoumont is decked out with a Nespresso coffee machine, boutique teas by Rubra and bathroom toiletries by Appelles Apothecary. There is a pillow menu and guests have access to a fitness centre.

Complimentary light breakfast, bicycle hire, fresh fruit, unlimited bottled water, WiFi and 11:00 checkout are all included. After a busy day exploring Fremantle, you can meet back at the lobby lounge for complimentary evening wine and cheese.

Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle also has a stylish Executive Boardroom decked out with state-of-the-art facilities and a dedicated crew.

description:
Esplanade Hotel Fremantle - by Rydges is located in the heart of Fremantle, overlooking Esplanade Park. 20 minutes' drive from central Perth, this hotel offers 2 outdoor pools and a fitness centre. A full buffet breakfast is available.

The hotel has 2 on-site restaurants with a great selection of international cuisine. The Atrium Garden Restaurant buffet serves a variety of special dishes, whilst The Harbour Master features tapas, grill and local seafood. Enjoy a drink in one of the 2 bars including, Marine Lounge Bar and the Ball & Chain with craft beer on tap and great pub-style food.

Guests enjoy a choice of spacious and comfortable guest rooms and suites, and some rooms offer a private balcony overlooking parklands. All rooms feature a 50-inch ULTRA HD LCD television with Streamcast

Esplanade Hotel by Rydges is within easy walking distance of local shops, restaurants, markets and museums. Fishing Boat Harbour is just 400 metres away and Fremantle Markets is just a 3-minute walk away. Perth International Airport is a 30-minute drive.

description:
Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle is a unique, boutique hotel, purpose-built using innovative sea container construction.

Fremantle Prison is a 10-minute walk away and Fremantle Markets is a 5-minute walk. The property is a 5-minute drive from the Western Australian Maritime Museum, and a 10-minute drive from Port Beach. Perth Airport is 40 minutes’ drive away.

Each stylish room at Hougoumont is decked out with a Nespresso coffee machine, boutique teas by Rubra and bathroom toiletries by Appelles Apothecary. There is a pillow menu and guests have access to a fitness centre.

Complimentary light breakfast, bicycle hire, fresh fruit, unlimited bottled water, WiFi and 11:00 checkout are all included. After a busy day exploring Fremantle, you can meet back at the lobby lounge for complimentary evening wine and cheese.

Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle also has a stylish Executive Boardroom decked out with state-of-the-art facilities and a dedicated crew.

Fremantle Prison is a 10-minute walk away and Fremantle Markets is a 5-minute walk. The property is a 5-minute drive from the Western Australian Maritime Museum, and a 10-minute drive from Port Beach. Perth Airport is 40 minutes’ drive away.

The Atrium Garden Restaurant buffet serves a variety of special dishes, whilst The Harbour Master features tapas, grill and local seafood. Enjoy a drink in one of the 2 bars including, Marine Lounge Bar and the Ball & Chain with craft beer on tap and great pub-style food.

Guests enjoy a choice of spacious and comfortable guest rooms and suites, and some rooms offer a private balcony overlooking parklands. All rooms feature a 50-inch ULTRA HD LCD television with Streamcast

Esplanade Hotel by Rydges is within easy walking distance of local shops, restaurants, markets and museums. Fishing Boat Harbour is just 400 metres away and Fremantle Markets is just a 3-minute walk away. Perth International Airport is a 30-minute drive.

description:
Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle is a unique, boutique hotel, purpose-built using innovative sea container construction.

Fremantle Prison is a 10-minute walk away and Fremantle Markets is a 5-minute walk. The property is a 5-minute drive from the Western Australian Maritime Museum, and a 10-minute drive from Port Beach. Perth Airport is 40 minutes’ drive away.

Each stylish room at Hougoumont is decked out with a Nespresso coffee machine, boutique teas by Rubra and bathroom toiletries by Appelles Apothecary. There is a pillow menu and guests have access to a fitness centre.

Complimentary light breakfast, bicycle hire, fresh fruit, unlimited bottled water, WiFi and 11:00 checkout are all included. After a busy day exploring Fremantle, you can meet back at the lobby lounge for complimentary evening wine and cheese.

Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle also has a stylish Executive Boardroom decked out with state-of-the-art facilities and a dedicated crew.

description:
Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle is a unique, boutique hotel, purpose-built using innovative sea container construction.

Fremantle Prison is a 10-minute walk away and Fremantle Markets is a 5-minute walk. The property is a 5-minute drive from the Western Australian Maritime Museum, and a 10-minute drive from Port Beach. Perth Airport is 40 minutes’ drive away.

Each stylish room at Hougoumont is decked out with a Nespresso coffee machine, boutique teas by Rubra and bathroom toiletries by Appelles Apothecary. There is a pillow menu and guests have access to a fitness centre.

Complimentary light breakfast, bicycle hire, fresh fruit, unlimited bottled water, WiFi and 11:00 checkout are all included. After a busy day exploring Fremantle, you can meet back at the lobby lounge for complimentary evening wine and cheese.

Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle also has a stylish Executive Boardroom decked out with state-of-the-art facilities and a dedicated crew.

Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle is a unique, boutique hotel, purpose-built using innovative sea container construction.

Fremantle Prison is a 10-minute walk away and Fremantle Markets is a 5-minute walk. The property is a 5-minute drive from the Western Australian Maritime Museum, and a 10-minute drive from Port Beach. Perth Airport is 40 minutes’ drive away.

Each stylish room at Hougoumont is decked out with a Nespresso coffee machine, boutique teas by Rubra and bathroom toiletries by Appelles Apothecary. There is a pillow menu and guests have access to a fitness centre.

Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle also has a stylish Executive Boardroom decked out with state-of-the-art facilities and a dedicated crew.

description:
Este YHA está situado en la división femenina de la prisión de Fremantle, declarada Patrimonio de la Humanidad, y ofrece habitaciones privadas y compartidas con conexión WiFi gratuita. Los huéspedes también pueden dormir en las celdas de la prisión.

El YHA Fremantle Prison fue construido en la década de 1850 y los primeros convictos lo ocuparon en 1855, hasta 1991, y ofrece habitaciones con baño privado o acceso a baño compartido. La mayoría tiene aire acondicionado. Se proporciona ropa de cama.

El establecimiento alberga una sala de juegos con mesa de ping pong. Hay una zona de salón compartida con TV y biblioteca.

description:
Esplanade Hotel Fremantle - by Rydges is located in the heart of Fremantle, overlooking Esplanade Park. 20 minutes' drive from central Perth, this hotel offers 2 outdoor pools and a fitness centre. A full buffet breakfast is available.

The hotel has 2 on-site restaurants with a great selection of international cuisine. The Atrium Garden Restaurant buffet serves a variety of special dishes, whilst The Harbour Master features tapas, grill and local seafood. Enjoy a drink in one of the 2 bars including, Marine Lounge Bar and the Ball & Chain with craft beer on tap and great pub-style food.

Guests enjoy a choice of spacious and comfortable guest rooms and suites, and some rooms offer a private balcony overlooking parklands. All rooms feature a 50-inch ULTRA HD LCD television with Streamcast

Esplanade Hotel by Rydges is within easy walking distance of local shops, restaurants, markets and museums. Fishing Boat Harbour is just 400 metres away and Fremantle Markets is just a 3-minute walk away. Perth International Airport is a 30-minute drive.

description:
Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle is a unique, boutique hotel, purpose-built using innovative sea container construction.

Fremantle Prison is a 10-minute walk away and Fremantle Markets is a 5-minute walk. The property is a 5-minute drive from the Western Australian Maritime Museum, and a 10-minute drive from Port Beach. Perth Airport is 40 minutes’ drive away.

Each stylish room at Hougoumont is decked out with a Nespresso coffee machine, boutique teas by Rubra and bathroom toiletries by Appelles Apothecary. There is a pillow menu and guests have access to a fitness centre.

Complimentary light breakfast, bicycle hire, fresh fruit, unlimited bottled water, WiFi and 11:00 checkout are all included. After a busy day exploring Fremantle, you can meet back at the lobby lounge for complimentary evening wine and cheese.

Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle also has a stylish Executive Boardroom decked out with state-of-the-art facilities and a dedicated crew.

El Rialto Apartments goza de una ubicación céntrica en el extremo oeste de la histórica localidad de Fremantle, a 10 minutos en coche de la playa de Fremantle. Ofrece alojamiento independiente con conexión WiFi gratuita y balcón.

El RIALTO SUITES Fremantle se encuentra a 10 minutos a pie del famoso Kailis Fish Market Cafe y de la cervecería Little Creatures Brewery. Los mercados de Fremantle están a solo 7 minutos a pie y el Museo Marítimo de Australia Occidental, a 6 minutos a pie. Se encuentra a 15 minutos en coche de la playa de Cottesloe y a 24 km del aeropuerto de Perth.

description:
Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle is a unique, boutique hotel, purpose-built using innovative sea container construction.

Fremantle Prison is a 10-minute walk away and Fremantle Markets is a 5-minute walk. The property is a 5-minute drive from the Western Australian Maritime Museum, and a 10-minute drive from Port Beach. Perth Airport is 40 minutes’ drive away.

Each stylish room at Hougoumont is decked out with a Nespresso coffee machine, boutique teas by Rubra and bathroom toiletries by Appelles Apothecary. There is a pillow menu and guests have access to a fitness centre.

Complimentary light breakfast, bicycle hire, fresh fruit, unlimited bottled water, WiFi and 11:00 checkout are all included. After a busy day exploring Fremantle, you can meet back at the lobby lounge for complimentary evening wine and cheese.

Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle also has a stylish Executive Boardroom decked out with state-of-the-art facilities and a dedicated crew.

description:
Esplanade Hotel Fremantle - by Rydges is located in the heart of Fremantle, overlooking Esplanade Park. 20 minutes' drive from central Perth, this hotel offers 2 outdoor pools and a fitness centre. A full buffet breakfast is available.

The hotel has 2 on-site restaurants with a great selection of international cuisine. The Atrium Garden Restaurant buffet serves a variety of special dishes, whilst The Harbour Master features tapas, grill and local seafood. Enjoy a drink in one of the 2 bars including, Marine Lounge Bar and the Ball & Chain with craft beer on tap and great pub-style food.

Guests enjoy a choice of spacious and comfortable guest rooms and suites, and some rooms offer a private balcony overlooking parklands. All rooms feature a 50-inch ULTRA HD LCD television with Streamcast

Esplanade Hotel by Rydges is within easy walking distance of local shops, restaurants, markets and museums. Fishing Boat Harbour is just 400 metres away and Fremantle Markets is just a 3-minute walk away. Perth International Airport is a 30-minute drive.

description:
Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle is a unique, boutique hotel, purpose-built using innovative sea container construction.

Fremantle Prison is a 10-minute walk away and Fremantle Markets is a 5-minute walk. The property is a 5-minute drive from the Western Australian Maritime Museum, and a 10-minute drive from Port Beach. Perth Airport is 40 minutes’ drive away.

Each stylish room at Hougoumont is decked out with a Nespresso coffee machine, boutique teas by Rubra and bathroom toiletries by Appelles Apothecary. There is a pillow menu and guests have access to a fitness centre.

Complimentary light breakfast, bicycle hire, fresh fruit, unlimited bottled water, WiFi and 11:00 checkout are all included. After a busy day exploring Fremantle, you can meet back at the lobby lounge for complimentary evening wine and cheese.

Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle also has a stylish Executive Boardroom decked out with state-of-the-art facilities and a dedicated crew.
